{
  "texts": [
    "However, LLMs have been transforming several organizations by driving them towards the paradigm of autonomous enterprise, characterized by the automation of numerous activities and operations.",
    "In this paradigm, ABPMSs play a pivotal role in supporting human tasks and decisions throughout all stages of the system life cycle.",
    "Starting from the business processes, LLMs are expected to embed the ability to overrun the local reasoning context, handle different scenarios, and improve the comprehension of the business activities within their outcomes [6].",
    "In front of the recognized potentiality of LLMs to assist human decisions in business context [1], this topic is few explored in literature [6] and to the best of our knowledge there is not an empirical validation about the effectiveness of LLMs for process-aware decision support.",
    "Starting from these considerations, this study introduces a novel approach to business process analysis and description based on the adoption of Large Language Models to implement a conversational process-aware DSS."
  ]
}